Specifically, users will be able

00:12:51.356 --> 00:12:53.986 A:middle
to open a photo in your app

00:12:54.256 --> 00:12:55.516 A:middle
without the need for you to

00:12:55.516 --> 00:12:57.296 A:middle
prompt for access to their

00:12:57.296 --> 00:12:59.116 A:middle
entire Photos library.

00:12:59.506 --> 00:13:02.956 A:middle
So, this will make them more

00:12:59.506 --> 00:13:02.956 A:middle
So, this will make them more

00:13:02.956 --> 00:13:04.706 A:middle
comfortable using your app,

00:13:05.326 --> 00:13:06.886 A:middle
because they will have better

00:13:06.886 --> 00:13:08.406 A:middle
control over their data.

00:13:09.526 --> 00:13:12.456 A:middle
We're also, adding a Write only

00:13:12.606 --> 00:13:14.476 A:middle
access to the Photos library.

00:13:15.286 --> 00:13:16.916 A:middle
So, for example, if there's a

00:13:16.916 --> 00:13:18.376 A:middle
game that wants to save a

00:13:18.376 --> 00:13:20.016 A:middle
screenshot of the user

00:13:20.016 --> 00:13:22.236 A:middle
achievements, it can prompt for

00:13:22.236 --> 00:13:24.906 A:middle
Write, but not Read access to

00:13:24.906 --> 00:13:25.736 A:middle
the Photos library.

00:13:26.496 --> 00:13:28.456 A:middle
And users might be more willing

00:13:28.456 --> 00:13:29.566 A:middle
to grant that request.

00:13:30.986 --> 00:13:32.176 A:middle
And because of these changes,

00:13:32.926 --> 00:13:37.136 A:middle
when users upgrade their devices

00:13:37.406 --> 00:13:39.916 A:middle
to iOS 11, existing apps will

00:13:39.916 --> 00:13:41.966 A:middle
re-prompt for access to the

00:13:41.966 --> 00:13:42.646 A:middle
Photos library.

00:13:43.386 --> 00:13:44.676 A:middle
If you want users to be able to

00:13:44.676 --> 00:13:47.006 A:middle
take advantage of this ability

00:13:47.006 --> 00:13:49.086 A:middle
to open Photos in your app

00:13:49.516 --> 00:13:52.476 A:middle
without being prompted, you can

00:13:52.476 --> 00:13:54.666 A:middle
adopt the Out Of Process Image

00:13:54.666 --> 00:13:56.706 A:middle
Picker, and to find out more,

00:13:57.206 --> 00:13:58.906 A:middle
please visit the Photos session.

00:13:59.326 --> 00:14:03.576 A:middle
This is a great way to add a

00:13:59.326 --> 00:14:03.576 A:middle
This is a great way to add a

00:14:03.666 --> 00:14:06.996 A:middle
photo in a user's profile or use

00:14:06.996 --> 00:14:08.016 A:middle
a photo in some other rare

00:14:08.016 --> 00:14:08.776 A:middle
action in your app.

