Now let's look at the Write 0nly

00:14:11.786 --> 00:14:12.366 A:middle
case.

00:14:13.846 --> 00:14:15.556 A:middle
There is a prompt and a Purpose

00:14:15.556 --> 00:14:17.566 A:middle
String, so if you want to adopt

