iOS 11 framework, which allows

00:14:36.876 --> 00:14:39.676 A:middle
your app to use NFC reader modes

00:14:40.136 --> 00:14:42.536 A:middle
to interact with nearby NFC

00:14:42.636 --> 00:14:42.886 A:middle
tags.

